summary: AN ORDINANCE authorizing the Mayor to execute an interlocal agreement between the City of Seattle and King County relating to King County's responsibility for the existing South Park Bridge and for replacing it and relating to potential annexation areas.
vote: 7-2 (In favor: Conlin, Della; Against: Clark, Drago, Godden, Licata, McIver, Rasmussen, Steinbrueck)
note: Final Full Council action was taken on December 11, 2006.
